2017-11-07T11:31:54.000Z","msg":"食個一次楊洲炒飯落洋蔥，d洋蔥仲要生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993a6c23ff24fcf9bc4bc1a1b74871c855181bf9","tid":457621,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「揚州炒飯標準」用料包括：<br />\n上等白米500克<br />\n雞蛋4個<br />\n海參20克<br />\n雞腿肉30克<br />\n火腿10克<br />\n干貝10克<br />\n蝦仁50克<br />\n花菇20克<br />\n鮮竹筍30克<br />\n青豆10克<br />\n蔥花10克<br />\n蝦籽1克<br />\n精鹽6克<br />\n紹酒6克<br />\n清雞湯100克<br />\n菜油60克</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n白米定白飯呀<br />\n500g米好撚多wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1580617041e3e9a5b573e519da446820ee94a2","tid":457621,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:03:22.000Z","msg":"鴛鴦炒飯<br />\n瑤柱蛋白炒飯<br />\n香芋臘味炒飯<br />\n福建炒飯"},{"pid":"65a2d82a8ca5f12240baf1ce499fb6986c8bf5d1","tid":457621,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:05:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>「揚州炒飯標準」用料包括：<br />\n上等白米500克<br />\n雞蛋4個<br />\n海參20克<br />\n雞腿肉30克<br />\n火腿10克<br />\n干貝10克<br />\n蝦仁50克<br />\n花菇20克<br />\n鮮竹筍30克<br />\n青豆10克<br />\n蔥花10克<br />\n蝦籽1克<br />\n精鹽6克<br />\n紹酒6克<br />\n清雞湯100克<br />\n菜油60克</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n白米定白飯呀<br />\n500g米好撚多wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊度定架??<br />\n揚州??<br />\n2002年，<span style=\"color: red;\">揚州市烹飪協會</span>根據《中國揚州菜》、《揚州菜點》、《淮揚風味》等菜譜中的敘述，同時參考了10多種食品工業標準，推出了「揚州炒飯標準」，屬於地方標準，有一定的強制性。但是此標準只對揚州市內餐館作出限制，若不按照標準來炒飯將會被摘牌[5]。而其他城市或國外廚師做揚州炒飯的材料並不受限。<br />\n「揚州炒飯標準」用料包括：<br />\n上等白米500克<br />\n......<br />\n菜油60克<br />\n<br />\n用揚州就當係自己發明<br />\n咁煮星洲炒米首先要問李光耀用咩材料?"},{"pid":"1080d73a4544df6bd22ab1d1c9f63ccc2c115bbb","tid":457621,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:08:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20151024/s00004/1445677606935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20151024%2Fs00004%2F1445677606935&d=CBPArazkphjuhTk%2BmDAdN8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=28f880bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20151024%2Fs00004%2F1445677606935&h=a2cfe980\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20151024/s00004/1445677606935</a><br />\n弱智 揚州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca16b946940e35b62b06dd30a54b05bcd584d9ae","tid":457621,"uid":4789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:09:59.000Z","msg":"寧願叫餐肉粒炒飯都唔叫揚州炒飯，揚州炒飯永遠食唔到一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcf96dd49f045b6b8dc676652256e3b52b79fba","tid":457621,"uid":139972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>生炒牛飯最穩陣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試生炒牛飯就知間野有冇料到</blockquote><br />\n邊一間最得?<br />\n記憶中未食過好食既生炒牛"},{"pid":"805785a1931815e543e9e78092c33b4d75f9dcc7","tid":457621,"uid":139972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:13:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>生炒牛飯最穩陣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgm